issue.title: Develop Product Design
issue.body:
Create a defined workflow and various graphics to convey the overall product design. 

**FULL TEAM ISSUE**

**DOD**:
- Graphic organizer showing the general workflow of the project
- Drawn images to show what each individual page might look like
- Each item documented and saved to the cloud via pictures/pdf

issue.title: Establish Product Description and Requirements
issue.body:
Brainstorm what our project is going to be, as well as what tasks are required to call the project 'complete'. 

**FULL TEAM ISSUE**

**DOD**:
- Product description written down and linked in issue
- Product requirements drafted into issues and assigned
- (Optional) Language/Framework decided

issue.title: Ice Breaker
issue.body:
Take 5 minutes for everyone to get to know each other a little bit. Also establish some vocab. such as: 

-DOD: Definition of Done
-Kotlin: Language used to develop applications in android studio
-Product: Overall creation during hackathon
-Project: Individual component of product

**DOD**:
-Everyone knows eachother's names
